g(x)=\prod_{k\ge 1,\,d\nmid k}\frac1{1-x^k}\;,\tag{1}
h(x)=\prod_{k\ge 1}(1+x^k+x^{2k}+\cdots+x^{(d-1)k})=\prod_{k\ge 1}\frac{1-x^{dk}}{1-x^k}\;.\tag{2}
